{"tid":698348,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"分手後發現懷孕 女教師涉於前度門外兩縱火","createTime":"2018-06-11T15:08:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T11:08:19.000Z","uid":29627,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e239b07e5e00d45fca2e5610e0f4135442aeb95b","tid":698348,"uid":29627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T15:08:13.000Z","msg":"分手後發現懷孕 女教師涉於前度門外兩縱火 <br />\n<br />\n 女教師與男友分手後赫然發現自己懷孕，疑有人拒絕負責，涉於上周五兩度到居於同一幢大廈的前男友門外燒報紙，令鐵閘損毀。女教師被控兩項縱火罪，案件今早在觀塘裁判法院提堂。<br />\n<br />\n被告梁菀晴（36歲）被控於上周五（6月8日）兩度在景林邨犯案，她報稱居於案發地點同一幢樓，比事主居所高3層。控方申請將案押後，以索取律政司法律意見，裁判官定於8月6日再訊。被告獲准以1萬元保釋外出。<br />\n<br />\n中出即飛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58304327\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58304327&d=MRtWvV%2BhC9yd2w7J3s%2Fj3tZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=37a80735\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180611%2F58304327&h=1d04e7db\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180611/58304327</a>"},{"pid":"f8ec0a4a08dcf2da42ef95e92d11c5e7d55dd5cc","tid":698348,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T16:09:27.000Z","msg":"有無驗清楚先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6523c055c8504d39e5763a9af1eaea7a6727587","tid":698348,"uid":51920,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-11T16:11:46.000Z","msg":"36歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji